 drivers/gpio/Makefile      |   1 +
 drivers/gpio/gpio-octeon.c | 166 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 175 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/gpio/gpio-octeon.c

